news.content:
Our next batch of Titan V2 3Nodes will ship in a matter of weeks.

Cheers! ü•Ç - to all that have pre-registered already and are making the internet a more sustainable and more private place!

Hurry up! üèÉüèΩ‚Äç‚ôÄÔ∏è - to all of you still looking for an easy way to become a ThreeFold Farmer.

You can order your Titan v2 on our pre-register page

And yes, all Titan's come with one of those rad stickers.
news.excerpt: Pre-register before the 30th of June if you want to be included in the batch.
